{"type": "article", "id": 14413, "title": "蘑菇餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-04T07:39:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000317HW7FPXQlI4UrsNaT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t 这套蘑菇形状的调料盒来自罗马尼亚的设计团队 Dragos Motica Studio ，灵感源于当地人在夏季的大雨天采蘑菇的传统。陶瓷的瓶身和木头做的蘑菇头非常柔和，大大小小排在一起组成了有趣的装饰。另外配有带小孔的盖子，在需要撒盐的时候换上，安全而卫生。这套餐具还带有定制托盘，配件都分开出售，在 13 欧到 33 欧之间。<a href=\"http://www.ubikubi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141948m4HnuiagbpTsQoCL.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"452\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141948Lpij6m8AvI0yVnUC.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"515\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141948zmYCHAnpbyB83Vhv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141950oFDA9sOtx3M4f6kr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}